javascript object vs json

 
1->json is a string format and js object is an object
2-> We can also send array in json format
3->undefined,function can not be sent into json 


json.stringify is use to translate your js object/data into jsonstring making it suitbale for travelling through mediums  and after that express.json is used to convert the json strinf data into its js object form 


app.use alag tareeke se use hota h ->keval initial strings of routes match karta h baki soch leta h ki nested mei mil jayega
app.use can use everything put,post,delete


app.put/app.get/app.post/app.delete -> alag tareeke se match hota h exactly wesa jesa hum sochte h poori poori route ki string match karta h 

why we use app.use(Express.json())
why we use JSON.stringify()